info.author: lucemia
info.name: ffmpeg-media-type
info.summary: ffmpeg-media-type is a Python library that utilizes FFmpeg to extract crucial details from media files, such as duration, width, and height. With seamless integration of 100% typehint support, it offers a user-friendly interface for easy access to media file information.
